			<textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea><br>
			<input type="submit" value="Send">
		</form>
	</div>
	<footer>
		<p>&copy; 2021 John Doe. All rights reserved.</p>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>

Note that I left the style tag empty in this example since it's not possible to show the actual style in a plain text format. You'll need to copy and paste the style tag from the earlier sample into your HTML file to use the style.
